name: 3D ICONS GEOMETRY PACK
description:
Hi everyone !


Lately I'm very interested in fancy design styles like geometry so I created a 3d kit pack that can be used in unique projects and I want to share it with everyone.

The icon should be zoomed out to see details.


Please share your opinion in the comments section and don't forget to hit the like button to support me in future projects.


-> Feel free to contact me for awesome design.
